outputs.output_descr: The overall objective of the project is to preserve democratic stability and a balance of power, promote the rule of law, and prevent new conflicts in the Kyrgyz Republic by providing support to the operationalization of the new Constitutional Chamber and creating an enabling environment, including positive public perception, for its smooth and proper functioning.

project_descr: New project on Support to Operationalization of the Constitutional Chamber of the Supreme Court of the Kyrgyz Republic
project_title: Support to Operationalization of Constitutional Chamber
